    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: March 7, 2026</p>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>This Privacy Policy describes how Melt Customer Support collects, uses, and protects your information when you contact us through our messaging services.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you message us, we collect:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Message content you send to us</li>
        <li>Your name and profile information from the messaging platform</li>
        <li>Timestamp of your messages</li>
        <li>Conversation history for customer service purposes</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information solely to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support</li>
        <li>Improve our customer service experience</li>
        <li>Follow up on previous conversations when necessary</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Protection</h2>
    <p>We take appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. Your messages are stored securely and accessed only by authorized customer support representatives.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties. Your information is used solely for providing customer support.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your conversation history for customer service purposes. You may request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt out of future communications</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your rights, please contact us through our messaging service or email us at privacy@melt-support.com.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 0.9em;">
        By using our messaging services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
    </p>
